{
  "texts": [
    "The underlying rationale is that many, or all, misaligned AI models capable of disempowering humanity will have the goal of disempowering humanity.",
    "Why should we believe that this is true?",
    "The canonical answer in the literature is the instrumental thesis (Bostrom 2012 (Bostrom, 2014)).",
    "The instrumental convergence thesis states that there are certain goals which are instrumentally useful for a wide range of final goals and a wide range of situations (Bostrom 2014, p. 109).",
    "Among these goals are self-preservation and the accumulation of power and resources."
  ]
}